    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/b01f1a24d698fb36ec5d250b1ed70795.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/b01f1a24d698fb36ec5d250b1ed70795.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/b01f1a24d698fb36ec5d250b1ed70795.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Embark on Your Epic Adventure in the World of Bitmates!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into <strong>Bitmates</strong>, a vibrant MMORPG where every choice you make shapes your destiny. Explore a vast fantasy world teeming with life, uncover its secrets, and craft your legend in a player-driven economy. Whether you're mastering life skills, taking down legendary bosses, or socializing with friends, Bitmates is the adventure you've been waiting for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/b6294b13fbaa5db699c938624e3d9d19.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/b6294b13fbaa5db699c938624e3d9d19.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a Vast, Beautiful World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From lush forests to arid deserts, explore a rich world with many environments, each crafted with love and detail. Discover hidden treasures, tackle unique challenges, and immerse yourself in the pixel-perfect art of this expansive world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/4b4303012ee98969dcc0643c4c941259.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/4b4303012ee98969dcc0643c4c941259.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/4b4303012ee98969dcc0643c4c941259.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master Every Skill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bitmates offers many skills that you can perfect. Every action contributes to your character's progression from fishing in serene lakes to forging powerful gear. With independent skill systems and endless synergies, your mastery defines your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/7a8bceb3ee62fbcc9bc051da39ac4479.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/7a8bceb3ee62fbcc9bc051da39ac4479.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/7a8bceb3ee62fbcc9bc051da39ac4479.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create Your Unique Identity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Express yourself with a vast collection of cosmetics. Stand out in the crowd with rare outfits and accessories, earned through gameplay or traded in the player-driven economy. Whether you’re a heroic warrior or a mystical alchemist, become your fantasy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/3d77095e2de8017a7d668a1d36953c7f.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/3d77095e2de8017a7d668a1d36953c7f.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/3d77095e2de8017a7d668a1d36953c7f.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Face Epic Boss Battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your mettle against colossal foes in thrilling, strategic combat. Whether solo or with allies, these encounters offer rare rewards and the chance to prove your skill. Are you ready to take on the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/26be5cd9263b6e7ff65cc4ecf4f56573.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/26be5cd9263b6e7ff65cc4ecf4f56573.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/26be5cd9263b6e7ff65cc4ecf4f56573.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage with a World Full of Stories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a rich history with unique NPCs and quests. Help villagers, uncover ancient mysteries, and make decisions that shape the world around you. Every region tells its own story—what role will you play?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/5d7d19d017e59032a700c0ad927b572b.poster.avif?t=1742423358\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/5d7d19d017e59032a700c0ad927b572b.webm?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154690/extras/5d7d19d017e59032a700c0ad927b572b.mp4?t=1742423358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Forge Lifelong Friendships</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bitmates thrives on community. Join friends for group activities, celebrate achievements, or simply relax in the serene towns. With vibrant social hubs, there’s always someone to share your adventure with.</p>",
